---
import Shell from '../layouts/Shell.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---
<Shell title="Refund Policy · DigitalChiselCo" description="DigitalChiselCo refund and return policy for digital STL file purchases.">
  <Breadcrumbs crumbs={[{ label: 'Refund Policy' }]} />

  <article class="prose prose-sm max-w-3xl text-ink-700">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl text-bronze-800 mb-6">Refund Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-xs text-ink-700/50 mb-8">Last updated: June 26, 2026</p>

    <p>We want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase. Please read our refund policy carefully before buying.</p>

    <h2>1. Digital Products — General Policy</h2>
    <p>Because all of our products are <strong>digital downloads</strong> delivered instantly after payment, we generally <strong>cannot offer refunds</strong> once the files have been downloaded or the download link has been accessed.</p>
    <p>This is standard practice for digital goods — once delivered, a digital file cannot be "returned."</p>

    <h2>2. When We Will Issue a Refund</h2>
    <p>We will gladly issue a <strong>full refund</strong> in the following cases:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Duplicate purchase:</strong> You accidentally bought the same file twice.</li>
      <li><strong>Corrupted or defective file:</strong> The downloaded file is damaged, cannot be opened, or does not match the product description — and we are unable to provide a working replacement.</li>
      <li><strong>Non-delivery:</strong> You did not receive your download link within 24 hours of payment and we cannot resolve the issue.</li>
      <li><strong>Technical error:</strong> A system error caused you to be charged incorrectly.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. How to Request a Refund</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Email us at <a href="mailto:jolly@digitalchiselco.com" class="text-bronze-600">jolly@digitalchiselco.com</a> within <strong>14 days</strong> of purchase.</li>
      <li>Include your <strong>order number</strong> (or the email used to purchase) and a brief description of the issue.</li>
      <li>We will review your request and respond within <strong>2 business days</strong>.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>4. Membership Plans</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Membership plans are <strong>one-time payments</strong> — not recurring subscriptions.</li>
      <li>If you have not accessed any membership files, we can issue a full refund within 14 days of purchase.</li>
      <li>Once membership files have been downloaded, the membership is considered used and is not eligible for a refund.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Non-Refundable Situations</h2>
    <p>Refunds will <strong>not</strong> be issued for:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Change of mind after downloading.</li>
      <li>Incompatibility with your specific CNC machine or software (file format and compatibility information is listed on every product page — please check before purchasing).</li>
      <li>Failure to download files before requesting a refund when download links are working.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>6. Refund Method</h2>
    <p>Approved refunds are processed through the original payment method. Depending on your bank or payment provider, it may take <strong>5–10 business days</strong> to appear on your statement.</p>

    <h2>7. Contact</h2>
    <p>Need help? Reach us at <a href="mailto:jolly@digitalchiselco.com" class="text-bronze-600">jolly@digitalchiselco.com</a>. We're real people and we read every message.</p>
  </article>
</Shell>
